<div style="background: #f4f4f4; padding: 20px;">
    <h1 style="color: #000000; text-align: center;">About Us</h1>

    <p style="color: #000000; line-height: 1.6;">Welcome to <strong>UrbanNest</strong>, your go-to destination for premium, stylish, and durable furniture. At UrbanNest, we believe that furniture is more than just functional—it’s an expression of your personality and lifestyle.</p>

    <h2 style="color: #000000; text-align: center;">Our Mission</h2>
    <p style="color: #000000; line-height: 1.6;">Our mission is to provide high-quality, contemporary furniture that transforms your home into a comfortable and elegant space. We blend aesthetics with functionality to bring you the best in modern furniture design.</p>

    <h2 style="color: #000000; text-align: center;">Why Choose Us?</h2>
    <ul style="list-style-type: none; padding: 0;">
        <li style="background: #FFD700; margin: 5px 0; padding: 10px; border-left: 5px solid #000000; color: #000000;"><strong>Quality Craftsmanship:</strong> We use premium materials and expert craftsmanship to ensure durability and comfort.</li>
        <li style="background: #FFD700; margin: 5px 0; padding: 10px; border-left: 5px solid #000000; color: #000000;"><strong>Affordable Luxury:</strong> Stylish furniture at competitive prices.</li>
        <li style="background: #FFD700; margin: 5px 0; padding: 10px; border-left: 5px solid #000000; color: #000000;"><strong>Eco-Friendly Approach:</strong> We focus on sustainability and environmentally friendly production methods.</li>
        <li style="background: #FFD700; margin: 5px 0; padding: 10px; border-left: 5px solid #000000; color: #000000;"><strong>Customer Satisfaction:</strong> Our customers are our priority, and we are dedicated to providing exceptional service.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="color: #000000; text-align: center;">Our Story</h2>
    <p style="color: #000000; line-height: 1.6;">UrbanNest was founded with a vision to redefine furniture shopping by making it seamless, enjoyable, and inspiring. Whether you're furnishing a new home or upgrading your space, we have the perfect pieces to match your style and needs.</p>

    <p style="color: #000000; line-height: 1.6;">Join us in creating beautiful and comfortable living spaces—because every home deserves the best!</p>
</div>

